    section#welcome
      .page-header
        h2 Welcome to VizSec 2006
      p The 4th International Workshop on Visualization for Cyber Security was held in Washington, DC, USA on November 3, 2006. VizSec brought together researchers and practitioners in information visualization and security to address the specific needs of the cyber security community through new and insightful visualization techniques.
      p VizSec was held in conjunction with the <a href='http://www.sigsac.org/ccs/CCS2006/'>13th ACM Computer and Communications Security Conference (CCS)</a>.
      p The proceedings are in the <a href="http://dl.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=1179576">ACM Digital Library</a>.

